          </span><span class="p" data-group-id="0162458515-393">{</span><span class="ss">debug_info</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">keep</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0162458515-393">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0162458515-369">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0162458515-368">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0162458515-367">}</span></code></pre><h2 id="generate-release-and-script-files" class="section-heading"><a href="#generate-release-and-script-files" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Generate release and script files</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="n">Erlang</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">OTP</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-1">[</span><span class="ss">erts</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">10.0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-1">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-2">[</span><span class="ss">source</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="ss">c13b302</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-2">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-3">[</span><span class="mi">64</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="ss">bit</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-3">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-4">[</span><span class="nc">smp</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-4">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-5">[</span><span class="nc">ds</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8254854028-5">]</spa